When: Thursday 29.01.2026 at 18.30 hours. <br/>
Duration: 1h30<br/>
<br/>
The London-based artist and writer Harun Morrison will be working with the students from DAS Theatre this January. In extension to his workshop, we are organizing a public talk to share Harun’s practice on symbiotic inhabitation and grafting with our wider community. Harun’s work often employs collaborative processes. His practice spans spatial design, text, video and sound.<br/>
<br/>
Find more info at our website! <br/>
<br/>
https://www.atd.ahk.nl/en/theatre-programmes/das-theatre/news/event/2026/1/29/a-talk-with-harun-morrison-symbiotic-inhabitation-embedding-and-grafting/<br/>
<br/>
(And more info in the comments) <br/>
<br/>
Please register for this talk via: maaike.boot@ahk.nl</p>]]></description>
